WITH PostStats AS (
    SELECT 
        Posts.Id AS PostId,
        Posts.Title,
        Posts.CreationDate,
        Posts.ViewCount,
        Posts.Score,
        Users.Reputation AS OwnerReputation,
        COUNT(DISTINCT Comments.Id) AS CommentCount,
        COUNT(DISTINCT Votes.Id) AS VoteCount
    FROM 
        Posts
    LEFT JOIN 
        Users ON Posts.OwnerUserId = Users.Id
    LEFT JOIN 
        Comments ON Posts.Id = Comments.PostId
    LEFT JOIN 
        Votes ON Posts.Id = Votes.PostId
    GROUP BY 
        Posts.Id, Posts.Title, Posts.CreationDate, Posts.ViewCount, Posts.Score, Users.Reputation
),
PostHistoryStats AS (
    SELECT 
        PostId,
        COUNT(*) AS HistoryCount,
        MAX(CreationDate) AS LastEdited
    FROM 
        PostHistory
    GROUP BY 
        PostId
)

SELECT 
    ps.PostId,
    ps.Title,
    ps.CreationDate,
    ps.ViewCount,
    ps.Score,
    ps.OwnerReputation,
    ps.CommentCount,
    ps.VoteCount,
    COALESCE(phs.HistoryCount, 0) AS PostHistoryCount,
    phs.LastEdited
FROM 
    PostStats ps
LEFT JOIN 
    PostHistoryStats phs ON ps.PostId = phs.PostId
ORDER BY 
    ps.ViewCount DESC, ps.Score DESC

GROUP BY "Posts"."Id", "Posts"."CreationDate", "Posts"."Score", "Posts"."ViewCount", "Posts"."Title", "Users"."Reputation") AS "t3" ON "t0"."PostId" = "t3"."POSTID"
ORDER BY "t3"."VIEWCOUNT" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t3"."SCORE" DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "t5"

SELECT COALESCE("Id", "Id") AS "Id", "PostId", "VoteTypeId", "UserId", "CreationDate", "BountyAmount"
FROM "Votes"

SELECT COALESCE("t5"."POSTID", "t5"."POSTID") AS "POSTID", "t5"."TITLE", "t5"."CREATIONDATE", "t5"."VIEWCOUNT", "t5"."SCORE", "t5"."OWNERREPUTATION", "t5"."COMMENTCOUNT", "t5"."VOTECOUNT", "t5"."POSTHISTORYCOUNT", "t5"."LASTEDITED"
FROM (SELECT "t3"."POSTID", "t3"."TITLE", "t3"."CREATIONDATE", "t3"."VIEWCOUNT", "t3"."SCORE", "t3"."OWNERREPUTATION", "t3"."COMMENTCOUNT", "t3"."VOTECOUNT", CASE WHEN "t0"."HISTORYCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t0"."HISTORYCOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "POSTHISTORYCOUNT", "t0"."LASTEDITED"
FROM (SELECT "PostId", COUNT(*) AS "HISTORYCOUNT", MAX("CreationDate") AS "LASTEDITED"
FROM "PostHistory"
GROUP BY "PostId") AS "t0"
RIGHT JOIN (SELECT MIN("Posts"."Id") AS "POSTID", "Posts"."Title" AS "TITLE", "Posts"."CreationDate" AS "CREATIONDATE", "Posts"."ViewCount" AS "VIEWCOUNT", "Posts"."Score" AS "SCORE", MIN("Users"."Reputation") AS "OWNERREPUTATION", COUNT(DISTINCT "Comments"."Id") AS "COMMENTCOUNT", COUNT(DISTINCT "s1"."Id") AS "VOTECOUNT"
FROM "Posts"
LEFT JOIN "Users" ON "Posts"."OwnerUserId" = "Users"."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Comments" ON "Posts"."Id" = "Comments"."PostId"
LEFT JOIN "s1" ON "Posts"."Id" = "s1"."PostId"
GROUP BY "Posts"."Id", "Posts"."CreationDate", "Posts"."Score", "Posts"."ViewCount", "Posts"."Title", "Users"."Reputation") AS "t3" ON "t0"."PostId" = "t3"."POSTID"
ORDER BY "t3"."VIEWCOUNT" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t3"."SCORE" DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "t5"
